title: Jets-Ravens TNF Preview, Pat McAfee Interview (Football 12/12)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Jets-Ravens on Thursday Night Football (4:30). The guys discuss how New York will game plan for a potentially limited Lamar Jackson, Baltimore's use of tight ends and Adam Gase's misuse of Sam Darnold before issuing player props and picks for the game. Then, Will is joined by former NFL punter and current sports media personality Pat McAfee (26:30) to discuss the Patriots' controversy, Urban Meyer, Adam Vinatieri, all-time punters and much more.
